message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product. It's truly exceptional and I believe it will greatly benefit you. Considering its value and quality, I propose a price of $16500 for this product. I hope we can come to an agreement that benefits both of us.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate the value and quality of your product. I would like to counteroffer a price of $15000 for the product.
